               <msContents>
                  <summary>Asmat prayer of the Seven Archangels, ድርሳን፡ ዘሰባቱ፡ ሊቃነ፡ መላእክት፡; Asmat Prayer of Mary, ጸሎት፡ ዘጸለየት፡ እግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡; Asmat Prayer for Drowning [Demons], ጸሎተ፡ መሥጥም፡, arranged for the days of the week; Computus of the Nights of Dǝmeṭǝros, ሐሳበ፡ ሌሊት፡ ዘድሜጥሮስ፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="6v" facs="002">Fols 1r–6v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer of the Seven Archangels, Dǝrsanä Zäsäbatu Liqǝnä Mäla’kǝt, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ድርሳን፡ ዘሰባቱ፡ ሊቃነ፡ መላእክት፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>

                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                         <locus from="1r" to="2r" facs="002">Fols 1r–2r</locus>
                         <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer of the Archangel Michael</title>

                      </msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                         <locus from="2r" to="2v" facs="003">Fols 2r–2v</locus>
                         <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer of the Archangel Gabriel</title>

                      </msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3">
                         <locus from="3r" to="3r" facs="004">Fols 3r–3r</locus>
                         <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer of the Archangel Rufael</title>

                      </msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4">
                         <locus from="4r" to="4r" facs="005">Fols 4r–4r</locus>
                         <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer of the Archangel Saquel</title>

                      </msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5">
                         <locus from="4v" to="5r" facs="006">Fols 4v–5r</locus>
                         <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer of the Archangel Fanuel</title>

                      </msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.6">
                         <locus from="5v" to="5v" facs="007">Fols 5v–5v</locus>
                         <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer of the Archangel Raguel</title>

                      </msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.7">
                         <locus from="6r" to="6v" facs="007">Fols 6r–6v</locus>
                         <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer of the Archangel Afnin</title>

                      </msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.8">
                         <locus from="6v" to="6v" facs="008">Fols 6v–6v</locus>
                         <title>Concluding Prayer</title>

                      </msItem>
                    </msItem>

                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                         <locus from="7r" to="10r" facs="008">Fols 7r–10r</locus>
                         <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat Prayer of Mary, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ ዘጸለየት፡ እግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡</foreign></title>
                         <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                         <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>ጸሎት፡ ዘጸለየት፡ እግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ወላዲተ፡ አምላክ፡ ጸሎታ፡ ወበረከታ፡ የሃሉ፡ ምስለ፡ ገብራ፡<gap reason="omitted"/> አርምሳድክኤል፡ አዶናኤል፡ ሮስ፡ ኪሮኮኤ፡ ያሶርኅ፡ ሮኅሮህዴኬ<gap reason="omitted"/>
                         </incipit>
                      </msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                         <locus from="10v" to="13v" facs="012">Fols 10v–13v</locus>
                         <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat Prayer for Drowning [Demons], <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎተ፡ መሥጥም፡</foreign></title>
                         <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                      </msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                         <locus from="13v" to="16v" facs="015">Fols 13v–16v</locus>
                         <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3851Hassab">We have written a
                                                  computus that we will remember in order not to
                                                  congregate with apostates...</title>
                         <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                         <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> እጽሕፍ፡ ሐሳበ፡ ሌሊት፡ ዘድሜጥሮስ፡ አበቅቴ፡ ሕፀዕ፡ ዕለት፡ በ፴ግዱፍ፡ ፩ሠናይ፡ በኩሉ፡ ግብር፡ በዝ፡ ሌሊት፡ ተፈጥሩ፡ አዳም፡ ወሄዋን፡ ዝራዕ፡ አዝርዕት፡ ወትክል፡ አትክልት፡ ወሑር፡ ፍኖተ፡ ወሕንፅ፡ ቤተ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                      </msItem>


               </msContents>
